    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo septuagesimo septimo, septimodecimo kl.
                        decembris, indictione undecima. Manifestus sum ego <persName><name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lambertus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Wido">Guidori</name></persName> filius quia per hanc cartulam
                        dono et trado tibi <persName><name ref="Matilda">Mattilde</name></persName>
                        filie <persName><name ref="Bonosus">Bonosti</name></persName> unam meam
                        videlicet petiam de terra que est campus cum arboribus et esse videtur in
                        loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/2120">Valiano</placeName>. Que
                        tenet unum caput in via publica et in terra <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3223"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti
                            Stefani</orgName> de <placeName ref="#places/2120" key="#Churches"
                            >Tassignano</placeName>, et alterum in terra et media fossa
                                <persName><name ref="Albertinus">Albertini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wiselbertus">Ghisalberti</name></persName>.
                        Latus unum tenet in via publica et alterum in terra et media fossa <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3224"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs> Sancti Bartholomei</orgName> et in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Laborator">Laboratoris</name></persName>. (…)
                            <foreign>Dimensioni</foreign>: cultras sex. (…) Pro qua donationem
                        recepi <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">launechil meritum anulum unum
                            aureum</rs>. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper penam
                        lib. centum denariorum lucensium. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luce</placeName>. (…) Hec autem cartula tali tenore facta est, si
                        vivente suprascripta Matilda predictus Lambertus mortuus fuerit, et post
                        unum annum post eius mortem, preteritis sexaginta diebus post inquisitionem,
                        aliquis eius heres dederint eidem Mattilde vel eius heredibus lib.
                        quadraginta octo bonorum lucensium denariorum, hec cartula evanesscat. Sin
                        autem in sua permaneat firmitate. Prenominatus Lambertus professus fuit se
                        habere nomine dotis pro suprascripta Mattilda lib. septuaginta denariorum et
                        libratas viginti guarnimentorum de dosso. Signum manus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardinus">Gerardini</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Montemagnus"
                            >Montemagni</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Signorellus"
                                >Signorelli</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Vivianus">Viviani</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandini</name></persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Bonusfilius">Bonusfilius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
